name: Professional Business Identity Mark - Logo Design
description:
This package includes: 
• Logo Design 

For your logo, you will receive: 
• Five initial logo concepts 
• Four rounds of revisions on your chosen concept 
• For each additional concept after five, the cost will be $25. 
• For each additional round of revisions after four, the cost will be $20.

Files included for your logo: 
• .ai - Adobe Illustrator format (Master File) 
• .eps - Another vector format for use with a broader range of vector programs 
• vector PDF file — excellent for printing; can be opened in Illustrator 
• High resolution Jpeg files in CMYK (for printing purposes) 
• High Resolution PNG files 
• Web Resolution Jpeg and PNG files (for internet use)
